<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy – {{ app_name }}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; max-width: 760px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; color: #222; line-height: 1.7; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.8em; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.2em; margin-top: 2em; color: #333; }
    a { color: #1a73e8; }
    .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9em; margin-bottom: 2em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="meta">
    Application: <strong>{{ app_name }}</strong><br>
    Developer: {{ developer_name }} (<a href="mailto:{{ developer_email }}">{{ developer_email }}</a>)<br>
    Effective date: {{ effective_date }}
  </p>

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how {{ developer_name }} ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and discloses
    information when you use <strong>{{ app_name }}</strong> (the "App"). By using the App you agree to this policy.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect personally identifiable information directly. However, the App uses third-party services
  that may collect information as described below.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Device identifiers</strong> – Android Advertising ID (GAID) and other resettable device identifiers, used for ad personalisation and frequency capping.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> – App crashes, performance metrics, and session information collected automatically to improve stability.</li>
    <li><strong>IP address</strong> – May be collected by ad networks for approximate geolocation-based ad targeting and fraud prevention.</li>
  </ul>

  {% if admob_enabled %}
  <h2>2. Advertising (Google AdMob)</h2>
  <p>
    The App is monetised with ads served by <strong>Google AdMob</strong>.
    {% if personalized_ads %}
    AdMob may use your Advertising ID to show personalised ads based on your interests.
    You can opt out of personalised advertising at any time by visiting your device's
    <strong>Settings → Google → Ads → Delete advertising ID</strong> (Android).
    {% else %}
    The App requests <strong>non-personalised ads only</strong>; no interest-based profiling is performed.
    {% endif %}
    Google's data practices are governed by the
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a>.
    We are not responsible for the content of advertisements served by AdMob or any linked
    third-party sites.
  </p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if content_disclaimer %}
  <h2>Content Accuracy</h2>
  <p>{{ content_disclaimer }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  <h2>3. Children's Privacy</h2>
  {% if directed_at_children %}
  <p>
    This App is directed at children under 13. We comply with the Children's Online Privacy
    Protection Act (COPPA). We do not knowingly collect personal data from children, and
    only non-personalised ads are served. Parents or guardians who believe their child has
    provided personal data should contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ developer_email }}">{{ developer_email }}</a>.
  </p>
  {% else %}
  <p>
    This App is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data
    from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided
    personal data, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.
  </p>
  {% endif %}

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We do not store personal data on our own servers. Data retained by third-party services
    (Google AdMob) is subject to their own retention policies.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Depending on your jurisdiction you may have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access, correct, or delete personal data held about you.</li>
    <li>Opt out of personalised advertising (see Section 2).</li>
    <li>Lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise these rights contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ developer_email }}">{{ developer_email }}</a>.</p>

  <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this policy from time to time. Changes are effective when posted on this page.
    The effective date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:{{ developer_email }}">{{ developer_email }}</a>.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
